{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, when he come from the war in the '20s, you must remember, when he was wounded, he was released.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in 1920, the Bolshevik invaded Poland, so he was called to the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the whole period of time since 1914 'til 1921, he was mostly on and off from the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't make any living, but my mother was very talented interior decorator, so she was supporting the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, we were living together in my grandfather-- Moses Goldfluss, my mother's father and and mother-- we were living in the beginning in their house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have a big farm not far away from city of Cracow in Podgorze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, when she started making a good living, we take apartment in-- in Podgorze, and its main street of Podgorze, street Podgorze.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not only in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Cracow has, in this particular period of time, close to about 60,000 but grew later on to about 75- 80,000 population before the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there quite [? many synagogues ?]  there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Main was the-- the temple, what that exists even today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the rest of them, small shuls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, dependent of your wealth and of your status in the community, you belonged to certain shuls, what have the similar group of Jews, prominent type of Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father belonged to the [INAUDIBLE] shul, to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- I was going to the shul 'til I became 18 years of age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And when I graduated from high school and went to the university, I went on the shul to the big holidays I-- on account of the sentiment and account of this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was still a conservative Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to the shul.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
